keyMappings:
unmap d
unmap J
unmap K
unmap b
unmap o

map <c-y> previousTab
map <c-u> nextTab

map dd removeTab
map u restoreTab

map J scrollPageDown
map K scrollPageUp

map  <c-h> goBack
map  <c-l> goForward

map bo closeOtherTabs
map <c-g> Vomnibar.activateInNewTab
map <c-e> Vomnibar.activateEditUrlInNewTab
